{
 "name": "RPlog_NRI_Interro_Montage",
 "title": "NRI Interrogation Montage",
 "summary": "In the aftermath of a ceremonial disaster, New Republic Intelligence agents interrogate the recovered victims-turned-suspects one by one in sterile interview rooms, recording their accounts of the abductions. The montage stitches together the increasingly absurd testimony of kitchen staff -- a nervous waiter, a four-armed chef, and others -- who recount how a half-open crate of unusually large eggs, left out in the sun, turned out to be very much alive. The agents grow steadily more befuddled as the witnesses' overlapping, contradictory, and bizarre stories paint a picture of chaos that defies easy investigation.",
